data.description: Beautiful home built by DoubleRock with a country feel yet close to town! This amazing 4 bedroom 2.5 bath home in located in Hadley Farms with No HOA! This home features and open floor plan with every womans dream kitchen. Granite countertops, beautiful custom cabinets and large island & Garden sink, Stainless steel appliances witha  luxury design. The light fixtures and detail in this home are breathtaking. Spacious family room with cozy wood burning fireplace & seperate office area, guest room or flex room. Also features a mud bench off the garage entrance, Walk in utility room with space for a freezer.  Large Master bedroom with dual sinks in the master bath with barn door entrance, seperate shower and garden tub & large walk in closet. Enjoy family gatherings on the covered patio while the kids play in the large backyard. Exterior features also include full irrigation system & rain gutters, Community offers playground, splash pad, soccer fields, walking trails!
